longBusinessSummary: Ola Electric Mobility Limited designs, manufactures, and sells electric vehicles in India. The company provides scooters, battery packs, motors, and vehicle frames in-house, including cells. It offers charging solutions. In addition, the company operates service centers and provides roadside assistance. Ola Electric Mobility Limited was incorporated in 2017 and is based in Bengaluru, India.
